# Corporate Ladder — Project Context

Telegram Mini App: climb the corporate ladder, avoid meetings/reorgs/deadlines. "Lumberjack meets modern office life."

## Stack

- Frontend: `apps/mini-app` (TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind) → Vercel
- API: `packages/api` (FastAPI) → Railway
- Bot: `apps/bot` (aiogram) → Railway
- DB: Supabase Postgres (`supabase/migrations/`)

## MVP v1 Scope

**Shipped:** core gameplay through **v1.8.5** (tagged `46abf19`), **v1.9.0** (F&F UX + OG adopt + onboarding), **v2.0.0** (triage + hardening). **Active:** **v2.1.0** retention sprint — code complete, tag/deploy pending — see [ROADMAP.md](../../ROADMAP.md) **Status**.

**Out:** Friends leaderboard (v1.1), All-time tab (v1.1), currency, skins, clans, quests, NFTs.

**Operational gate:** F&F window → [docs/FF_EXECUTION.md](../../docs/FF_EXECUTION.md); DEVICE_QA v2.0 + Vercel OG redeploy. Match ROADMAP § Shipped baseline (v1.5 → v1.8.5) plus [CHANGELOG 1.9.0](CHANGELOG.md#190---2026-06-14), [2.0.0](CHANGELOG.md#200---2026-06-14), and `[Unreleased]`.

**Monetization (optional):** AdsGram rewarded revive on qualifying game-over — no virtual currency or forced interstitials. See [docs/ads-acquisition-plan.md](../../docs/ads-acquisition-plan.md).

## Principles

1. **Humor is the product** — preserve satirical tone in all copy.
2. **No secrets in frontend** — bot token and Supabase service key stay on Railway only.
3. **Minimal scope** — do not add v1.1 features without explicit approval.
4. **Match shipped spec** — [ROADMAP.md](../../ROADMAP.md) § Shipped baseline; scope gates in [docs/mvp-scope.md](../../docs/mvp-scope.md). Historical ROADMAP gates → [docs/archive/ROADMAP_HISTORY.md](../../docs/archive/ROADMAP_HISTORY.md); v0.1 origin → [docs/archive/](../../docs/archive/) only when researching.
5. **Terminology** — UI uses Energy / Deadline; code obstacle type `burnout` unchanged.

## Family

Sibling repo: [DITreneris/site](https://github.com/DITreneris/site) (Prompt Anatomy marketing). Shared doc/changelog/verifier habits; this repo keeps satirical Telegram game scope.

